Package: gitpins
Type: Package
Title: Pin urls to local file and version with git
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Magnus Thor Torfason
Maintainer: Magnus Thor Torfason <m@zulutime.net>
Description: Quickly download an online resource and make it available
    for R as a local file. Repeated downloads are versioned using
    a local git repository, and if getting a document from the web
    is not successful, a previous local download is made available.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: 
    digest,
    gert,
    here,
    jsonlite
Suggests: 
    tibble,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
URL: https://github.com/torfason/gitpins
BugReports: https://github.com/torfason/gitpins/issues
